+    begin
+        // [FEATURE] [Planning Worksheet] [Action Message Filter]
+        // [SCENARIO] When a filter is set on Action Message field (e.g., Cancel) and Carry Out Action Message is executed,
+        // only the filtered lines should be processed. Lines with other Action Messages should remain.
+        Initialize();
